title: #19 - That Episode with Your Manhattan Dating Tour Guide, Tiff Baira
description:
She’s the post-millennial version of Sex and the City…. except she’s here to help guide you through YOUR dating and relationship questions!

This week’s guest is Tik Tok influencer and dating coach Tiff Baira. She hosts Take Me Out, a podcast that follows Tiff as she defines what it means to date in New York on her own terms.

Together, they answer this week’s dating questions.

Follow Tiff on TikTok

Follow Tiff on Instagram

Visit Tiff’s website to learn how to work one-on-one with her.

Check out Tiff’s podcast, “Take Me Out”
